parameters: Fake Adventurer Psema: Now, you can't escape anymore.

Fake Adventurer Psema: So you're going to put up a fight,
huh? Well, I guess I'll have to go easy on you, just enough
to make it interesting.
Do you want to skip the adult scene?

Do you want to retry the battle?※ If you choose No, it will
result in a game over.

Psema the Fake Adventurer: Tch, your futile resistance...
I've had enough, I'll kill you before I [use] you!

Clea: Who do you think you are, trying to kill me? I won't
die until I see the dragon die, no matter what!
Fake Adventurer Psema: Who do you think I am?
Fake Adventurer Psema: Kuuh, the Adventurer's Guild...!

Fake Adventurer Psema: Damn, this is a big loss if it
continues like this.
Fake Adventurer Psema: I won't forget your faces!
Clea: Please... \| don't leave me alone...
Adventurer Celis: Are you calm now?

Adventurer Celis: No... it's okay. I'm sorry for turning you
away even though you came to the Adventurer's Guild.

Clea: No, it's okay. Nobody in the village believes me
either.

Clea: They say I went crazy from the shock of my parents
being killed.

Adventurer Celis: ...So your goal is to defeat the dragon,
huh?
Clea: Do you believe me, Celis-san?

Adventurer Celis: If you look at the scar on my back, and
because nobody believes in my dream either.

Adventurer Celis: I might understand your feelings a little
bit.

Clea: Celis-san, don't you find it difficult to carry your
dreams alone?

Adventurer Celis: I became an adventurer so that I wouldn't
give up on myself and wouldn't lose to loneliness.
Clea: ...So that I wouldn't give up on myself.
Clea: What is your dream, Celis-san?
Adventurer Celis: It's a secret for now.

Adventurer Celis: If you were to have a dream that you
wanted to pursue with all your heart and soul.

Adventurer Celis: Someday, let's talk about our dreams
here...

Adventurer Celis: I think with this, you can take the exam
to join the Adventurer's Guild.

Adventurer Celis: If you truly wish to achieve your goals
with your own hands, then I'll be waiting for you at the
Adventurer's Guild.

Clea (I never imagined fighting with my own self that I
never even thought about)
Clea (But if no one believes in me and no one helps me)
Clea (I'll do it. I'll avenge my father and mother!)
Adventurer Celis: Can't you walk alone?
Clea: I'm fine, I can walk!

Clea (I'll become a strong adventurer like Celis-san and
defeat the dragon!)
実績 クレアの誓い
Girl Mel: Is Clea's song over with this?
Bard: Hahaha, I said it was a special song, didn't I?
Girl Mel: Yeah, I'm looking forward to the continuation!
Girl Mel: By the way, what is the name of this song?

Bard: The name may change depending on the bard, but I'll
use my favorite one.

Bard: The story of the girl Clea, who was spoken of as the
hero of the empire... The name of that song is...!
